_:Nc8c4a27bd1ce42b395fc79adbaa19648 <http://schema.org/name> "The Rt Hon Laura Trott MBE MP" .
_:Nc8c4a27bd1ce42b395fc79adbaa19648 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Laura Trott was Chief Secretary to the Treasury between 13 November 2023 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Work and Pensions between 27 October 2022 and 13 November 2023.</p>\n" .
